high_descs: Turn to the right and turn left to the counter.
Pick up the sponge from the counter.
Carry the sponge and take a step to the right.
Place the sponge in the pot on the counter.
Pick up the pot from the counter.
Carry the pot and turn to the right to find the sink.
Place the pot in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a pot and sponge to the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go between the kitchen island and the counter top, on the left just past the stove, then turn right towards the counter top on your left.
Pick up the green sponge on the front, right corner of the counter top.
Move over to the corner of the counter, on your right.
Place the sponge in the pan near the edge of the counter.
Pick up the pan with the sponge inside it.
Turn to the sink on your right.
Place the pan with the sponge inside it, in the center of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put  pan containing a sponge in the sink.

high_descs: turn right and walk to the right side of the stove on your left
grab the sponge off of the counter to the right of the stove
move to the right a bit and face the kitchen counter
place the sponge inside of the pan on the kitchen counter
pick up the pan off of the counter
turn right to face the kitchen sink
place the pan inside of the right side kitchen sink
anns.task_desc: place a pan with a sponge in it in the sink on the right
